sql:
SELECT build_name, species, assembly_date 
FROM genome_builds 
WHERE build_name = 'GRCh37';

external_knowledge:
- Mutations refer to changes in the DNA sequence of an organism; 
- Genome builds are versions of a genome assembly; 
- Quality metrics are measures used to evaluate the accuracy or reliability of data; 
- Annotations are notes or labels added to data to provide additional context or information.

